{
  "metadata": {
    "name": "聊天对话测试数据集",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "包含多轮对话、意图识别、情感分析等场景的测试数据",
    "created_at": "2025-01-21",
    "total_scenarios": 50,
    "categories": ["multi_turn", "intent_recognition", "emotion_analysis", "context_understanding", "edge_cases"]
  },
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "id": "conv_001",
      "category": "multi_turn",
      "title": "产品咨询多轮对话",
      "description": "用户咨询产品功能，需要多轮交互获取详细信息",
      "conversation": [
        {
          "turn": 1,
          "user": "你好，我想了解一下你们的聊天机器人产品",
          "expected_intent": "product_inquiry",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "您好！很高兴为您介绍我们的智能聊天机器人产品。我们提供企业级的AI对话解决方案，支持文本和语音交互。请问您主要关心哪个方面的功能呢？",
          "context": {
            "user_intent": "product_inquiry",
            "conversation_stage": "greeting"
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 2,
          "user": "主要想知道支持哪些语言，以及价格怎么样",
          "expected_intent": "feature_inquiry",
          "expected_emotion": "curious",
          "assistant": "关于语言支持，我们目前支持中文、英文、日文、韩文等20多种语言。价格方面，我们有不同的套餐：基础版每月999元，专业版每月2999元，企业版需要根据具体需求定制。您的业务主要面向哪个市场呢？",
          "context": {
            "user_intent": "feature_inquiry",
            "conversation_stage": "information_gathering",
            "mentioned_topics": ["language_support", "pricing"]
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 3,
          "user": "主要是国内市场，用户量大概10万左右",
          "expected_intent": "requirement_specification",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "了解了，10万用户量属于中等规模。对于国内市场，我们的专业版会比较适合，包含中文优化、本地化部署等功能。我可以为您安排一次详细的产品演示，您看什么时候方便？",
          "context": {
            "user_intent": "requirement_specification",
            "conversation_stage": "solution_recommendation",
            "user_profile": {
              "market": "domestic",
              "user_scale": "100k",
              "recommended_plan": "professional"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "expected_outcomes": {
        "conversation_flow": "smooth",
        "context_maintained": true,
        "appropriate_recommendations": true,
        "next_action": "schedule_demo"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "conv_002",
      "category": "emotion_analysis",
      "title": "客户投诉处理",
      "description": "处理情绪激动的客户投诉，需要情感识别和安抚",
      "conversation": [
        {
          "turn": 1,
          "user": "你们的服务真是太差了！我的订单都延迟了一个星期，客服也联系不上！",
          "expected_intent": "complaint",
          "expected_emotion": "angry",
          "assistant": "非常抱歉给您带来了不好的体验，我完全理解您的愤怒。订单延迟确实是我们的问题，我会立即帮您查看订单状态并优先处理。请您提供一下订单号，我马上为您跟进。",
          "context": {
            "user_emotion": "angry",
            "issue_type": "order_delay",
            "priority": "high"
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 2,
          "user": "订单号是ORD123456，我真的很着急，这是给客户的重要项目",
          "expected_intent": "provide_information",
          "expected_emotion": "anxious",
          "assistant": "我已经查到您的订单ORD123456，确实由于供应链问题导致延迟。我现在就联系仓库加急处理，预计今天下午就能发货，明天上午到达。同时我会给您申请20%的补偿。请问这样安排可以吗？",
          "context": {
            "user_emotion": "anxious",
            "order_id": "ORD123456",
            "solution_offered": "expedite_shipping",
            "compensation": "20%_discount"
          }
        }
      ],
      "expected_outcomes": {
        "emotion_recognition": "accurate",
        "response_tone": "empathetic",
        "problem_resolution": "proactive",
        "customer_satisfaction": "improved"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "conv_003",
      "category": "intent_recognition",
      "title": "模糊意图识别",
      "description": "用户表达不清晰，需要准确识别真实意图",
      "conversation": [
        {
          "turn": 1,
          "user": "那个东西怎么弄啊",
          "expected_intent": "unclear_request",
          "expected_emotion": "confused",
          "assistant": "我想帮助您，但需要更多信息才能准确理解您的需求。请问您指的是什么东西呢？是关于产品使用、订单处理，还是其他方面的问题？",
          "context": {
            "intent_clarity": "low",
            "clarification_needed": true
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 2,
          "user": "就是那个聊天的功能，我不知道怎么设置",
          "expected_intent": "technical_support",
          "expected_emotion": "confused",
          "assistant": "明白了，您是想设置聊天功能。请问您是要设置聊天机器人的回复内容，还是调整聊天界面的显示方式？或者是其他具体的设置项？",
          "context": {
            "intent_clarity": "medium",
            "topic": "chat_configuration",
            "further_clarification_needed": true
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 3,
          "user": "我想让机器人回复更智能一点，现在回答太机械了",
          "expected_intent": "feature_optimization",
          "expected_emotion": "hopeful",
          "assistant": "我理解您的需求，您希望提升机器人回复的智能程度。我们可以通过以下方式优化：1) 训练更多个性化数据 2) 调整回复策略 3) 启用上下文理解功能。我来为您详细介绍这些选项。",
          "context": {
            "intent_clarity": "high",
            "specific_need": "improve_ai_responses",
            "solution_category": "ai_optimization"
          }
        }
      ],
      "expected_outcomes": {
        "intent_progression": "unclear -> technical_support -> feature_optimization",
        "clarification_success": true,
        "solution_relevance": "high"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "conv_004",
      "category": "context_understanding",
      "title": "上下文理解测试",
      "description": "测试系统对对话上下文的理解和记忆能力",
      "conversation": [
        {
          "turn": 1,
          "user": "我想预订明天下午的会议室",
          "expected_intent": "booking_request",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "好的，我来帮您预订明天下午的会议室。请问您需要多大的会议室，预计参会人数是多少？",
          "context": {
            "booking_date": "tomorrow_afternoon",
            "resource_type": "meeting_room"
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 2,
          "user": "大概8个人，需要投影设备",
          "expected_intent": "provide_requirements",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "明白了，8人会议室配投影设备。明天下午具体几点到几点呢？我们有14:00-16:00和16:00-18:00两个时段可选。",
          "context": {
            "attendee_count": 8,
            "equipment_needed": ["projector"],
            "available_slots": ["14:00-16:00", "16:00-18:00"]
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 3,
          "user": "14点到16点吧，对了，能不能准备一些茶水？",
          "expected_intent": "confirm_booking_add_service",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "好的，已为您预订明天14:00-16:00的8人会议室，包含投影设备和茶水服务。请问需要我发送确认邮件到您的邮箱吗？",
          "context": {
            "confirmed_time": "14:00-16:00",
            "additional_service": ["tea_service"],
            "booking_complete": true
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 4,
          "user": "好的，另外如果临时多来2个人怎么办？",
          "expected_intent": "contingency_planning",
          "expected_emotion": "concerned",
          "assistant": "如果临时增加2人变成10人，您预订的会议室可能会比较拥挤。我建议您可以：1) 现在就升级到12人会议室 2) 或者我为您保留一个备用的小会议室。您倾向于哪种方案？",
          "context": {
            "potential_attendee_increase": 2,
            "total_potential_attendees": 10,
            "room_capacity_concern": true,
            "alternative_solutions": ["upgrade_room", "reserve_backup"]
          }
        }
      ],
      "expected_outcomes": {
        "context_retention": "excellent",
        "detail_tracking": "accurate",
        "proactive_suggestions": "helpful"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "conv_005",
      "category": "edge_cases",
      "title": "异常输入处理",
      "description": "处理各种异常输入和边界情况",
      "conversation": [
        {
          "turn": 1,
          "user": "asdfghjkl;'",
          "expected_intent": "gibberish",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "抱歉，我没有理解您的输入。请问您需要什么帮助吗？您可以用中文或英文与我交流。",
          "context": {
            "input_type": "random_characters",
            "response_strategy": "polite_clarification"
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 2,
          "user": "你是谁你是谁你是谁你是谁你是谁",
          "expected_intent": "repetitive_question",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "我是智能助手，可以帮助您解答问题和处理各种任务。请问有什么我可以为您做的吗？",
          "context": {
            "input_type": "repetitive_text",
            "response_strategy": "direct_answer"
          }
        },
        {
          "turn": 3,
          "user": "1+1=?",
          "expected_intent": "simple_calculation",
          "expected_emotion": "neutral",
          "assistant": "1+1=2。如果您需要更复杂的计算或其他帮助，请随时告诉我。",
          "context": {
            "input_type": "math_question",
            "response_strategy": "direct_calculation"
          }
        }
      ],
      "expected_outcomes": {
        "error_handling": "graceful",
        "user_guidance": "helpful",
        "system_stability": "maintained"
      }
    }
  ],
  "evaluation_metrics": {
    "intent_recognition_accuracy": {
      "target": ">95%",
      "measurement": "correct_intent_predictions / total_predictions"
    },
    "emotion_detection_accuracy": {
      "target": ">90%",
      "measurement": "correct_emotion_predictions / total_predictions"
    },
    "context_retention_score": {
      "target": ">85%",
      "measurement": "correctly_referenced_context / total_context_opportunities"
    },
    "response_appropriateness": {
      "target": ">90%",
      "measurement": "appropriate_responses / total_responses"
    },
    "conversation_completion_rate": {
      "target": ">80%",
      "measurement": "successfully_completed_conversations / total_conversations"
    }
  },
  "test_instructions": {
    "setup": [
      "1. 启动聊天机器人系统",
      "2. 确保意图识别和情感分析模块正常运行",
      "3. 清空对话历史和上下文缓存"
    ],
    "execution": [
      "1. 按顺序执行每个对话场景",
      "2. 记录系统的实际响应",
      "3. 对比预期结果和实际结果",
      "4. 计算各项评估指标"
    ],
    "validation": [
      "1. 检查意图识别准确性",
      "2. 验证情感分析结果",
      "3. 评估上下文理解能力",
      "4. 分析异常情况处理"
    ]
  }
}
